{"type": "article", "id": 40579, "title": "这款随身听，会让你重拾对磁带的热情吗？｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-05-08T23:11:03Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 267, "name": "平面设计"}, {"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 566, "name": "手机"}, {"id": 3505, "name": "口罩"}, {"id": 6205, "name": "邮票"}, {"id": 7158, "name": "壁灯"}, {"id": 40208, "name": "休闲椅"}, {"id": 40209, "name": "磁带"}, {"id": 15672, "name": "Marcel Wanders"}, {"id": 40210, "name": "Moshe Safdie"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 19, "praise_count": 251, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170508173806yRMZNnAdup6q3K2t.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「<b>BestDesign</b>」或是「<b>Qthings</b>」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Daydream by Assaf Israel </h3><p>位于米兰和特拉维夫的设计工作室 JOYNOUT 的创始人 Assaf Israel，最近设计了一款名为“Daydream”的拼插休闲座椅，极具雕塑感，其外形的灵感来源于无穷大符号∞的形状。这款座椅可以提供单人就坐、躺卧或两人共同就坐互动的方式，<a href=\"http://www.designboom.com/design/assaf-israel-daydream-lounger-joynout-milan-design-week-05-03-2017/\" rel=\"nofollow\">设计师说</a>：“在人际关系逐渐疏远的世界中，我们希望利用 Daydream 拉近人与人之间的距离。”它既可以应用于公共场所，也能在私密空间中使用。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170508173903YfEnBS1dKlGMOp0X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.613692\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170508173903XObEcSF6sr0ULG7a.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.645477\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170508173903WiXsCj1uZ4LUwozO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.584352\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201705081739045tAfbr6lEZskIRXj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.361111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170508173904U4pfgrvVLduAXsBh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.655257\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170508173905eZqIbt3u90JzEAoW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.720049\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.designboom.com/design/assaf-israel-daydream-lounger-joynout-milan-design-week-05-03-2017/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Designboom</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>The Elbow Clip-on Cassette Player by BrainMonk</h3><p>说起音乐界的复古潮流，首先想到的大概就是黑胶唱片了。但在我们儿时的记忆中，磁带也占据着很重要的位置。立陶宛视听艺术组织 BrainMonk 最近就为磁带量身而造了一款名为“Elbow”的播放器，打破了原先录音机、随身听的外观样式，采用相当简化的手法，直接为磁带套上了一个驱动磁带的双向旋转电机。通过中间位置的旋钮，用户可以操作磁带正反面播放，或是实现快进、快退等功能。不过，Elbow 目前还停留在概念阶段，并未量产。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170508174035D7m2sKQulVbfwqjy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.530562\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170508174035hU6qYV5MOFKbnxtL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707824\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170508174035h30OUaPAsFHSYrxi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.738386\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170508174036DTPKp2ciVjlUJ4Sr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.733496\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017050817403694ZXwez7OKnvjaTd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.706601\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201705081740364dz9Slj2AoI8P6Kb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.652812\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170508174036VG4HT0I193bnoeuX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707824\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://elbow.co.nf/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Elbow 官网</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>O2Today Air Pollution Mask by Marcel Wanders</h3><p>空气污染已成全球性的议题。最近，就连荷兰设计大师 Marcel Wanders 也涉足了口罩设计领域，他与总部位于旧金山的 O2TODAY 公司合作，推出了一款舒适且时尚的防污染口罩。它的创新之处在于采用了一种特殊的样貌材料，可以制成空气过滤器，能过滤 95% 的有害大气颗粒物，同时相较于大多数防雾霾口罩来说，又保持了良好的透气性。它提供 6 种不同的图案，零售价为 34 美元，根据不同地区的污染水平，每个口罩大约可以佩戴 15 至 45 天。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170508174221BHpuEUfOYjxLoPW6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.647208\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170508174222gyPibvsBxpuNR6LI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.631557\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170508174221Zkln16aSM0mpJ7bf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.635364\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017050817422236hDJTZdkALNOS9H.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.629865\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201705081742236tC1fyr3BiZuTEmA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.628596\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170508174222TcV3kUlFomI8h2NS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.637479\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170508174243aTYIdDA93qozOtkQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000423\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2017/05/02/marcel-wanders-design-air-pollution-masks-graphic-prints-o2today/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Commemorative Stamp by Moshe Safdie</h3><p>为庆祝加拿大建国 150 周年，以及 1967 年在魁北克举办的万国博览会 50 周年，加拿大邮政总局邀请加拿大建筑大师 Moshe Safdie，合作设计了一款纪念邮票，主题为加拿大蒙特利尔圣罗伦斯河畔标志性的建筑 Habitat 67 集合住宅，其总设计师恰是 Moshe Safdie。造此建筑的目的是为了给中低收入阶层提供社会福利住宅，将每一盒子式的住宅单元都设定为统一的模块，然后预制建造出来，再像集装箱那样以参差错落的形式堆积起来。这次以 Habitat 67 为主题的这张邮票也是总共推出的 10 张邮票中的第一张。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170508174332hZEl0bU14wi9HqYa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170508174332XeCjcEDHIp2bSKgT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.754717\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.archdaily.com/870317/canada-post-commemorates-canadas-150th-anniversary-with-habitat-67-stamp\" rel=\"nofollow\">Archdaily</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Minimalist Light Phone by Joe Hollier &amp; Kaiwei Tang</h3><p>两个在 Google 30 周年活动上结识的年轻人 Joe Hollier 和 Kaiwei Tang，抱着想让人们摆脱智能手机束缚的想法，设计了一款极简手机 Light Phone，主要功能是用来拨打和接听电话，配备了点阵 LED 和简单的键盘触摸模块、扬声器、麦克风、以及音量控制按键，续航时间可达 20 天左右。它仅有 4 毫米厚，如一张银行卡般大小。它另有一个特别功能是，智能手机壳通过 App 与 Light Phone 连接，显示智能手机上的来电，同时又隔绝了大量智能手机上的信息干扰。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170508174420cYu1GTo4eyQsb2ka.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563034\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170508174420KovLtT75q0yPOjsG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.909052\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170508174420UekDrAsgSRZz1Y8i.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667090\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170508174420wnfMxWIbCi50vXoq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.895939\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170508174421NOEGJDS8HuRB1nyf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2017/05/06/minimalist-light-phone-design-used-little-as-possible-mobile-technology/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Slice Wall Lamps by Yuval Tzur</h3><p>来自特拉维夫的产品设计师 Yuval Tzur ，带来的新作是一款名为“Slice”的装饰性壁灯，据称其灵感来源于 1980 年代的俱乐部场景，高饱和度的色彩被大胆运用。Slice 系列可以以不同的组合方式，不同的色彩搭配方式挂于墙壁上，装饰性极强，可以为空间增添不少俏皮、轻松的意味。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170508174515bf0BRzlkNcSgp5qG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170508174514pNJRjxQU8aLi71EM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170508174516P2Blx4HIgc5Tnktz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.361111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170508174516MofdVs4ShZrPGbOL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170508174517Typ8v0MtPOf5QDHk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170508174517kjQrbnZu5pJgeaWH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.designboom.com/design/yuval-tzur-slice-tel-aviv-05-05-2017/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Designboom</a></figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\"><br></p>"}